Detailed Description

The Display Subsystem (DSS) provides the logic to interface display peripherals. DSS has multiple hardware blocks and in order to simplify DSS programming, DSS CSL FL driver has been logically divided into following modules:

  • DSS Top (See Top Level CSL FL)
  • DSS Common (See DSS Common CSL FL)
  • DSS Video Pipe (See DSS Video Pipe CSL FL)
  • DSS Overlay (See DSS Overlay CSL FL)
  • DSS Video Port (See DSS Video Port CSL FL)
